## 2. Dynamic Search & Discovery (Phase 2)
Transitioning from matching raw strings to a structured product/variant hierarchy.

### Component: [Search Logic]
- [MODIFY] [db.ts](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/lib/db.ts):
    - **2.1 Normalization**: Debounce input (300ms). Handle synonyms/typos.
    - **2.2 Intent Parsing**: If query matches known groups (e.g. "stanley"), return ALL results. Don't auto-create 1 fake product.
    - **2.3 Link Fix**: Generate routes using `productId` (`/products/[id]`), NOT search text slugs.
- [MODIFY] [products/page.tsx](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/app/products/page.tsx):
    - **2.4 Infinite Scanning**: Add 5s timeout. If no results, show "No sustainable matches found" + clear error UI.
    - **2.5 Recommendations**: Link "Recommended for You" to user history and favored categories in [UserProfile](file:///C:/Users/sarbr/Desktop/Antigravity/Projects/SustainaBuy_v0.2/lib/db.ts#20-29).

